ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.group

Class PPV_PCA_GOAL

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.group.PPV_PCA_GOAL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class PPV_PCA_GOAL
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a PPV_PCA_GOAL group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: GOL (Goal Detail)
    • 2: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    • 3: VAR (Variance) optional repeating
    • 4: PPV_PCA_GOAL_ROLE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 5: PPV_PCA_GOAL_PATHWAY (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 6: PPV_PCA_GOAL_OBSERVATION (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 7: PPV_PCA_PROBLEM (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 8: PPV_PCA_ORDER (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
